	    clean up code.
	
	* imap/mailimap.c
	    update message count with EXPUNGE responses.
	
	* tools/mailstream_socket.c
	    added comment about initial state of socket.
	
	* tools/mailstream_ssl.c
	    added comment about initial state of socket.
	    read() is fixed.
	    
